[Tokino Sora Birthday Party 2026]

3
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:48,500
高鳴る心臓に祈りを乗せて
Placing a prayer upon my throbbing heart,

4
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:51,300
曖昧な夢を描く
I draw an ambiguous dream.

5
00:02:51,300 --> 00:02:54,000
幻想は想像のまま
If fantasy remains just an imagination,

6
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:57,200
終われないんだ
it cannot end like this.

7
00:03:01,300 --> 00:03:04,500
みんな、今日見に来てくれてありがとう！
Everyone, thank you so much for coming to watch today!

8
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:10,000
答えを延々と探し続けて
Endlessly searching for the answer,

9
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:12,700
何者かになりたくて
wanting to become someone,

10
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:17,800
潸々と降る夕立をただ眺めた
I merely stared at the pouring evening shower.

11
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:22,900
優しく寄り添って心が晴れるのなら
If gently being by your side clears up my heart,

12
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:27,400
翼が生えたような気がして
I feel as though wings have grown on me,

13
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:31,500
いつだって隣にいるから
because I'll always be by your side.

14
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:38,200
だって言葉紡いで唄うことがわたしの運命だ
Because spinning words and singing is my destiny.

15
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:44,000
世界にありふれた虚しささえも上書きして
Overwriting even the emptiness common in this world,

16
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:49,800
路地裏に咲いた花のように願いを照らす
it illuminates my wishes like a flower blooming in a back alley,

17
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:55,700
小さな光に憧れて
