27
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:52,000
どうか歌よ響いて
Please, let my song resonate!

28
00:04:54,600 --> 00:05:00,500
あぁ心臓の鼓動が今日もうるさい
Ah, the beating of my heart is loud today too...

29
