行き止まりばっか足が竦んで立てないよ
I'm always hitting dead ends, my legs freeze and I can't stand.

30
00:05:05,988 --> 00:05:11,388
音のない世界から君を見つけて連れ出すんだ
I'll find you in this soundless world and lead you out.

31
00:05:12,088 --> 00:05:16,388
言葉紡いで唄うことがわたしの運命だ
Weaving words together to sing is my destiny.

32
00:05:16,388 --> 00:05:22,388
世界にありふれた虚しささえも上書きして
Overwriting even the emptiness so common in this world.

33
